atmu: At MuVet we understand the specialbond you share with your pets, and our mission is to provide top-notch veterinary services tailored to meet their unique needs.
h11: Our veterinarian will check your pet's weight, temperature, pulse, and respiration rate. Vets will scan your pet for any obvious signs of illness and will likely ask you questions about your pet's normal behavior.
h22: Planning to travel with you your pet? We've got you covered, our clinic will assist you in prepairing any travelling papers for your pet, ensuring a smooth and hassle-free journey for you and your companion.
h33: Our skilled veterinary team is rquipped to handle a wide range of surgical procedures, From routine surgeries to specialized interventions, we prioritize the health and well-being of your pets.
ali2: A veterinarian graduated from the Jordanian University of Science and Technology with 3 years of experience in puppy, cats and surgeries.
